![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3993a903-c47d-4e19-89fd-9ee38ea341e8/e354.jpg)

It's that time spooky time of the year and we’re diving fangs-first into the swan song that is _Venom: The Last Dance!_ Join us as we break down the final tale that sees Eddie Brock face off against some intense inner demons (and outer ones, too). We’re talking symbiote drama, Knull, insane battles, and give our thoughts about the franchise as a whole. If you’re into anti-heroes, cosmic chaos, or just can’t get enough of the wild side of Marvel, tune in – it’s going to be a blast!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

